name: Dawson College
street: 3040 Rue Sherbrooke Ouest Westmount QC H3Z 1A4 Canada
directions:
Gender neutral restrooms are in 2E wing and 5B wing.  2 and 5 indicate the floor they are located on.
Either from De Maisonneuve entrance to access 2E wing or from Sherbrooke entrance (must walk up outdoor stairs) to access 5B wing restroom.  It is on the left.
From Atwater metro, simply go through the Dawson entrance, wall straight and up the escalator which leads to the 2nd floor.  Turn right then straight.

For hospital visitors, but it's a busy place.

Both entrances are easy.
